Hey guys,
Here is a new map from me.
I made a jail map with 16 jails (16 terrorist spawns) and some ct spawns.
There is a big wall to play some games like spraycontest or chickenfight.
Then there is a swimming hall with cool springboards.
Next to the swimming hall is a disco with 4 cool songs an some lighting effects.
check this out ;)
